text.section:
Moneys in the fund shall be held in an interest-bearing account and shall be used as follows and for no other purposes:
To reclaim, in the event of forfeiture, permit areas or increments thereof, covered by the fund;
To compensate the cabinet for costs of administering the fund;
To fund audits and actuarial studies required under KRS 350.509; and
To cover all operating expenses and any necessary legal expenses of the Reclamation Guaranty Fund Commission.
